OL,3,C80s rock icon Mike Peters dies from
OL,4,Cblood cancer at the age of 66
OL,6,FThe frontman of rock band The Alarm
OL,7,Fhas died at the age of 66.
OL,9,FMike Peters had been fighting an
OL,10,Faggressive form of blood cancer for 30
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FThe band's US tour was cancelled in
OL,14,F2024 after Peters noticed that a lump
OL,15,Fin his neck had appeared overnight.
OL,17,FDoctors quickly realised the star had
OL,18,Fdeveloped Richter's syndrome, where
OL,19,FCLL changes into a much more
OL,20,Faggressive lymphoma.
