OL,3,C80s rock icon Mike Peters dies from
OL,4,Cblood cancer at the age of 66
OL,6,FLater that year, the musician had
OL,7,Fannounced he was in remission from
OL,8,Fchronic slow-growing lymphocytic
OL,9,Fleukaemia (CLL), a type of cancer of
OL,10,Fthe blood and bone marrow.
OL,12,FBut the Welsh music icon died on the
OL,13,Fevening of 28 April 2025 surrounded by
OL,14,Fhis family.
OL,16,FPeters leaves his wife Jules, 58, and
OL,17,Ftwo sons, Dylan, 20, and Evan, 18.
OL,19,FBorn in Prestatyn, North Wales, Peters
OL,20,Foften played in support of causes
OL,21,Fclose to where he lived.
