OL,3,C80s rock icon Mike Peters dies from
OL,4,Cblood cancer at the age of 66
OL,6,FThe musician, who supported the likes
OL,7,Fof U2 and Status Quo on tour, first
OL,8,Frose to fame in the early 1980s with
OL,9,FThe Alarm with anthems like '68 Guns'
OL,10,Fand 'Strength' gathering international
OL,11,Facclaim.
OL,13,FAlongside his wife, he co-founded Love
OL,14,FHope Strength, a cancer charity to
OL,15,Fencourage action around stem cell
OL,16,Fdonation.
