OL,3,C80s rock icon Mike Peters dies from
OL,4,Cblood cancer at the age of 66
OL,6,FThrough its Get On The List campaigns,
OL,7,Foften publicised at rock concerts, the
OL,8,Fcharity has added more than 250,000
OL,9,Fpeople to stem cell registers
OL,10,Fworldwide.
OL,12,FMike Peters and The Alarm recorded the
OL,13,FWelsh football team's official song
OL,14,Ffor EURO 2020 ` 'The Red Wall of
OL,15,FCymru' ` that saw him sing the song
OL,16,Fwith fans across the country.
OL,18,FPeters was a passionate fan of Welsh
OL,19,Ffootball and performed live in the
OL,20,Fstadium ahead of Men's National Team
OL,21,Fmatches.
