OL,3,C80s rock icon Mike Peters dies from
OL,4,Cblood cancer at the age of 66
OL,6,FReacting to the news, Ian Gwyn Hughes,
OL,7,Fthe FAW's Head of Public Relations &
OL,8,FCulture, said "Often seen at the side
OL,9,Fof the pitch at the Cardiff City
OL,10,Fstadium before matches, Mike was
OL,11,Fhumble, always positive and smiling.
OL,13,F"He will not only be remembered for
OL,14,Fhis music but also as just a proper,
OL,15,Fgenuine football fan who made a huge
OL,16,Fcontribution to the culture of The Red
OL,17,FWall. Our sympathies to his family"
